o%20properly%20introduce%20viewers%20to%20Negan%20(played%20by%20Jeffrey%20Dean%20Morgan)%20after%20teasing%20him%20for%20the%20entire%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20what%20an%20introduction%20it%20was.%20After%20terrorizing%20our%20main%20characters%20off-screen%2C%20Negan%20realized%20he%20couldn't%20decide%20who%20to%20kill%20and%20used%20a%20game%20of%20Eenie%20Meenie%20to%20pick%20his%20victim%20in%20the%20episode%20%26quot%3BLast%20Day%20on%20Earth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20we%20didn't%20get%20to%20see%20his%20selection%20%E2%80%94%20instead%2C%20the%20camera%20switched%20to%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20the%20victim%2C%20who%20was%20then%20viciously%20bludgeoned%20by%20Negan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EViewers%20didn't%20find%20out%20until%20season%20seven%20who%20was%20on%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20Lucille's%20wrath.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EYou%20might%20not%20think%20of%20%26quot%3BStar%20Trek%3A%20The%20Next%20Generation%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20show%20capable%20of%20cliffhangers%2C%20but%20when%20Captain%20Jean-Luc%20Picard%20was%20turned%20into%20a%20Borg%2C%20viewers%20worldwide%20were%20desperate%20for%20the%20next%20season.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221678%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22captain%20jean%20luc%20picard%20star%20trek%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659c7fe86979d73718217f7e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221259%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPatrick%20Stewart%20in%20%26quot%3BStar%20Trek%3A%20The%20Next%20Generation.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EParamount%20Domestic%20Television%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20design%2C%20%26quot%3BStar%20Trek%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20fairly%20episodic%20show.%20But%20when%20the%20season%20three%20finale%20aired%20in%20June%201990%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20even%20%26quot%3BStar%20Trek%26quot%3B%20knows%20the%20power%20of%20a%20good%20cliffhanger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20season%20ended%20with%20the%20episode%20%26quot%3BThe%20Best%20of%20Both%20Worlds%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20which%20Jean-Luc%20Picard%20(Patrick%20Stewart)%2C%20the%20brave%20captain%20of%20the%20Enterprise%2C%20is%20taken%20captive%20by%20an%20evil%20alien%20species%20called%20the%20Borg%2C%20who%20have%20the%20power%20to%20eventually%20take%20over%20the%20galaxy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20Picard's%20friend%20and%20first%20officer%2C%20William%20Riker%20(Jonathan%20Frakes)%2C%20is%20left%20with%20a%20choice%3A%20Does%20he%20mount%20a%20rescue%20mission%20or%20take%20the%20opportunity%20to%20wipe%20out%20the%20Borg%2C%20Picard%20included%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20episode%20concludes%20with%20Riker%20firing%20on%20the%20Borg's%20ship%20before%20hitting%20us%20with%20a%20%26quot%3BTo%20be%20continued%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%20leaving%20Picard's%20fate%20up%20in%20the%20air%20until%20season%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhen%20the%20door%20of%20the%20hatch%20was%20blown%20off%20its%20hinges%20in%20the%20season%20one%20finale%20of%20%26quot%3BLost%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20became%20clear%20this%20wasn't%20just%20a%20show%20about%20a%20group%20of%20plane%20crash%20survivors.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221845%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22john%20and%20jack%20on%20lost%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659c85cdec62ab5daf81c08b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221384%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELocke%20and%20Jack%20on%20%26quot%3BLost.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EABC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20first%20season%20of%20%26quot%3BLost%26quot%3B%20in%202004%20and%202005%2C%20fans%20kept%20getting%20hints%20that%20this%20island%20was%20not%20your%20typical%20deserted%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20episode%20%26quot%3BExodus%2C%26quot%3B%20when%20Jack%20(Matthew%20Fox)%20and%20Locke%20(Terry%20O'Quinn)%20finally%20blow%20the%20door%20off%20a%20mysterious%20hatch%20they%20found%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20jungle%20and%20realize%20that%20it%20went%20deep%20underground%2C%20we%20get%20confirmation%3A%20Something%20is%20wrong%20on%20this%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Walt%20(Malcolm%20David%20Kelley)%2C%20a%20young%20boy%20on%20the%20plane%2C%20is%20snatched%20from%20a%20rescue%20raft%20by%20a%20mysterious%20group%20of%20people%20known%20only%20as%20the%20Others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20retrospect%2C%20it's%20wild%20that%20we%20had%20to%20wait%20months%20to%20find%20out%20who%20took%20Walt%20and%20what%20was%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20hatch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETwo%20seasons%20later%2C%20the%20rug%20was%20pulled%20out%20from%20under%20%26quot%3BLost%26quot%3B%20fans%20again.%20Two%20words%3A%20Flash-forwards.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jack%20flash%20forward%20lost%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659c85c21c5c7b8c9a0f0b18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22570%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJack%20on%20%26quot%3BLost.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EABC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20first%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BLost%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20was%20clear%20each%20episode%20would%20split%20the%20action%20between%20the%20present-day%20happenings%20on%20the%20island%20and%20flashbacks%2C%20usually%20focused%20on%20one%20survivor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20season%20three%20finale%2C%20%26quot%3BThrough%20the%20Looking%20Glass%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20aired%20in%202007%2C%20seemed%20different.%20We%20watched%20as%20Jack%20(Fox)%20became%20heavily%20depressed%2C%20even%20suicidal%2C%20and%20hooked%20on%20painkillers%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20a%20previously%20unknown%20part%20of%20Jack's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20last%20scene%20of%20the%20finale%20showed%20us%20the%20truth%20%E2%80%94%20this%20wasn't%20a%20flashback%2C%20but%20a%20flash-%3Cem%3Eforward%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20letting%20us%20know%20that%20at%20least%20Jack%20and%20Kate%20(Evangeline%20Lilly)%20would%20be%20rescued%20from%20the%20island%20at%20some%20point%20in%20the%20future%20and%20that%20Jack%20would%20tearfully%20tell%20Kate%20that%20they%20have%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20island%2C%20thus%20changing%20the%20course%20of%20%26quot%3BLost%26quot%3B%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%201980%2C%20it%20was%20impossible%20to%20watch%20TV%20without%20CBS%20asking%2C%20%26quot%3BWho%20shot%20JR%3F%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221199%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jr%20dallas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659c85ba6979d73718218014%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22899%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJR%20Ewing%20on%20%26quot%3BDallas.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECBS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20%26quot%3BDallas%26quot%3B%20had%20entered%20its%20third%20season%2C%20audiences%20were%20captivated%20by%20the%20wheeling%20and%20dealing%20of%20the%20Ewing%20oil%2Fcattle%20dynasty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20no%20character%20was%20more%20admired%20(or%20reviled)%20than%20JR%20Ewing%20(Larry%20Hagman)%2C%20a%20scheming%20oil%20tycoon%20who%20stopped%20at%20nothing%20to%20get%20what%20he%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20season%20three%20finale%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20House%20Divided%2C%26quot%3B%20concluded%20with%20JR%20getting%20shot%20by%20a%20mystery%20gunman%2C%20TV%20audiences%20became%20consumed%20by%20the%20question%2C%20%26quot%3BWho%20shot%20JR%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20could've%20been%20anyone%2C%20as%20everyone%20on%20the%20show%20had%20a%20reason%20to%20kill%20JR.%20In%20fact%2C%20everyone%20on%20the%20show%20was%20filmed%20shooting%20JR%20to%20keep%20it%20a%20secret%20from%20audiences%20and%20the%20crew%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20four%20episodes%20of%20season%20four%20before%20the%20shooter's%20identity%20was%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Simpsons%26quot%3B%20poked%20fun%20at%20%26quot%3BDallas%26quot%3B%20with%20its%20own%20two-part%20episode%2C%20%26quot%3BWho%20Shot%20Mr.%20Burns%3F%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width