3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20they%20did%20%E2%80%94%20until%20the%20season%20two%20finale%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Telling%2C%26quot%3B%20in%202003.%20After%20surviving%20a%20particularly%20nasty%20fight%2C%20Sydney%20wakes%20up%20in%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20asking%20for%20Vaughn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20arrives%2C%20only%20to%20tell%20Sydney%20that%20she's%20been%20missing%20for%20two%20years%2C%20and%20in%20that%20time%2C%20he's%20married%20someone%20else.%20A%20true%20gut%20punch%2C%20even%2021%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20could%20there%20be%20a%20%26quot%3BBuffy%20the%20Vampire%20Slayer%26quot%3B%20without%20Buffy%3F%20Fans%20were%20forced%20to%20ask%20this%20question%20after%20the%20fifth%20season%20finale.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221133%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22buffy's%20gravestone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659c8610ec62ab5daf81c098%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22850%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BBuffy%20the%20Vampire%20Slayer.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EThe%20WB%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20titular%20vampire%20slayer%2C%20Buffy%20(Sarah%20Michelle%20Gellar)%2C%20gave%20more%20of%20herself%20than%20any%20teenager%20should%20be%20expected%20to%20throughout%20the%20first%20five%20seasons%20of%20%26quot%3BBuffy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20season%20five%20finale%20in%202001%2C%20titled%20%26quot%3BThe%20Gift%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20sacrificed%20herself%20to%20save%20her%20sister%20Dawn%20(Michelle%20Trachtenberg)%2C%20her%20friends%2C%20and%20the%20town%20of%20Sunnydale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20episode's%20final%20shot%20is%20a%20close-up%20of%20Buffy's%20gravestone%2C%20which%20declares%2C%20%26quot%3BShe%20saved%20the%20world.%20A%20lot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20could%20there%20be%20a%20season%20six%20of%20%26quot%3BBuffy%26quot%3B%20without%20Buffy%3F%20Fans%20were%20asking%20this%20question%20until%20the%20show%20came%20back%20for%20season%20six%20when%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20Buffy's%20death%20would%20have%20long-term%20consequences%20for%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20sixth%20season%20of%20%26quot%3BER%26quot%3B%20in%202000%20employed%20a%20rare%20midseason%20cliffhanger%20when%20a%20patient%20attacked%20John%20Carter%20and%20Lucy%20Knight.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221491%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22er%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659c86631c5c7b8c9a0f0b29%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221118%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BER.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENBC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20first%20episode%20(%26quot%3BBe%20Still%20My%20Heart%26quot%3B)%2C%20Lucy%20Knight%20(Kellie%20Martin)%20is%20trying%20to%20tell%20her%20boss%2C%20Dr.%20John%20Carter%20(Noah%20Wyle)%2C%20that%20she's%20concerned%20about%20the%20mental%20state%20of%20her%20patient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%2C%20busy%20with%20other%20things%2C%20ignores%20her%2C%20with%20disastrous%20consequences.%20The%20patient%20stabs%20both%20of%20them%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20episode%20ending%20in%20a%20haunting%20image%20of%20John%20and%20Lucy%20staring%20at%20each%20other%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20next%20to%20a%20hospital%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20nothing%20compared%20to%20what%20happened%20the%20following%20week%20when%20their%20colleagues%20found%20them%20in%20this%20state%20in%20the%20episode%20%26quot%3BAll%20in%20the%20Family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-famous-cliffhangers-tv-history%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705327561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659c89f11c5c7b8c9a0f0b5b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-famous-cliffhangers-tv-history%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BER%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BLost%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BFriends%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BGame%20of%20Thrones%26quot%3B%20all%20have%20one%20thing%20in%20common%3A%20legendary%20cliffhangers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Gabbi%20Shaw)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-famous-cliffhangers-tv-history%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Search%20of%20Answers%20for%20the%20Manipur%20Violence%2C%20a%20New%20Book%20Takes%20a%20Deep%20Dive%20into%20the%20Conflict%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04085450%2FFvO7YL1aEAAlR43.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20worthwhile%20to%20mention%20that%20Nandita%20Haksar%20is%20the%20daughter%20of%20the%20legendary%20late%20P.N.%20Haksar%2C%20who%20was%20the%20principal%20secretary%20to%20the%20then%20prime%20minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20for%20many%20years.%20He%20was%20practically%20a%20philosopher%20and%20guide%20to%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20was%20initially%20uncertain%20and%20inexperienced%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%20at%20a%20young%20age%2C%20so%20she%20depended%20on%20P.N.%20Haksar%2C%20who%20also%20had%20a%20bond%20with%20her%20being%20a%20Kashmiri%20Pandit%20like%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20Haksar%20was%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20liberation%20of%20Bangladesh%20in%201971.%20Indira%20Gandhi%20was%20wavering%2C%20but%20it%20was%20the%20advice%20of%20Haksar%20who%20emboldened%20her%20to%20take%20a%20decisive%20decision%20to%20liberate%20Bangladesh.%20I%20remember%20the%20unforgettable%20words%20of%20former%20president%20K.R.%20Narayan%20who%20said%20in%20his%20condolence%20message%2C%20%E2%80%9CLate%20Mr.%20PN%20Haksar%20was%20the%20brightest%20star%20among%20the%20galaxies%20of%20Stars.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20forward%20to%20the%20book%20%3Cem%3ELet%20Freedom%20Rings%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20A.S.%20Atai%20Shimray%2C%20Nandita%20Haksar%20wrote%3A%20whenever%20she%20introduced%20her%20husband%20as%20a%20Naga%2C%20many%20often%20asked%20who%20are%20Nagas%3F%20Nandita%20was%20a%20little%20tired%20of%20always%20explaining%20about%20Nagas%20and%20later%20on%20she%20told%20them%3B%20%E2%80%9Cif%20you%20want%20to%20know%20about%20the%20Nagas%20read%20Asterix.%E2%80%9D%20Perhaps%20she%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20indomitable%20spirits%20of%20the%20Naga%20people%20like%20the%20Gauls.%20Emperor%20Julius%20Caesar%20conquered%20half%20of%20the%20known%20world%2C%20but%20his%20mighty%20soldiers%20could%20not%20defeat%20a%20small%20French%20tribe%2C%20the%20Gauls.%20Something%20similar%20to%20the%20Gaul%2C%20the%20British%20Empire%20defeated%20the%20strongest%20Indian%20tribes%2C%20the%20Sikhs%20or%20the%20Marathas%20in%20less%20than%2020%20years.%20However%2C%20the%20British%20took%20over%2040%20years%2C%20from%201832%20to%201879%2C%20to%20defeat%20the%20Nagas.%20In%20the%20final%20battle%20with%20the%20Khonoma%20warriors%2C%20the%20British%20soldiers%2C%20numbering%20over%203%2C000%2C%20were%20led%20by%20a%20Brigadier%20General%20Nation.%20The%20Khonoma%20warriors%20had%20just%20500%20guns%2C%20and%20the%20British%20soldiers%20met%20their%20match%20in%20the%20Khonoma%20warriors.%20The%20indomitable%20spirits%20of%20the%20Khonoma%20warriors%20were%20a%20subject%20of%20study%20at%20North%20Eastern%20Hill%20University%20(NEHU).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-reasons-failure-and-solution-q-and-a%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20Behind%20the%20Manipur%20Violence%20and%20Why%20Stopping%20It%20Poses%20a%20Test%20For%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20four%20books%20published%20in%20the%20past%20eight%20months%20regarding%20the%20ethnic%20clash%20in%20Manipur%2C%20three%20books%20authored%20by%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20people%20were%20promptly%20banned%20by%20the%20state%20government%20of%20Manipur.%20I%20found%20the%20book%20%3Cem%3EShooting%20the%20Sun%20%3C%2Fem%3Emost%20insightful%20from%20an%20incisive%20mind%2C%20written%20with%20great%20empathy%2C%20balanced%2C%20objective%20but%20hard-hitting.%20Like%20Nandita%2C%20her%20book%20is%20candid%2C%20forthright%2C%20and%20unapologetic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20338px)%2085vw%2C%20338px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15191514%2Fbook-pic.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22338%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15191514%2Fbook-pic.jpg%20593w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15191514%2Fbook-pic-234x300.jpg%20234w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693098%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22433%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EShooting%20the%20Sun%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20Nandita%20Haskar.%20Publisher%3A%20Speaking%20Tiger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20title%20of%20the%20book%20%3Cem%3EShooting%20The%20Sun%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20taken%20from%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20Meitei%20epics%2C%20%3Cem%3ENumit%20Kappa%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20translated%20by%20T.C.%20Hodson%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Meitheis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(London%201908).%20The%20book%20tells%20of%20the%20violent%2C%20cruel%2C%20and%20infused%20with%20unadulterated%20savagery.%20In%20her%20words%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20hate%20and%20rage%20are%20tangible%20and%20there%20is%20no%20way%20to%20make%20the%20stories%20any%20less%20brutal%E2%80%99.%20In%20the%20opening%20of%20her%20book%2C%20she%20mentioned%20her%20life%20in%20Manipur%20while%20representing%20the%20Poumai%20Nagas%2C%20victims%20of%20human%20rights%20violations%20committed%20by%20the%20Indian%20security%20forces%20during%20the%20counter-insurgency%20operation%20code-named%20Bluebird%20in%201987%2C%20and%20her%20friendship%20with%20Maharaj%20Kumari%20Binodini%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20the%20Manipur%20King%2C%20Sir%20Maharaj%20Churachand%20Singh.%20Throughout%20the%20book%2C%20she%20has%20flagged%20many%20uncomfortable%20questions.%20She%20admitted%20she%20had%20no%20illusion%20in%20writing%20this%20book%20given%20the%20likelihood%20of%20a%20strong%20reaction%20from%20the%20affected%20community.%20According%20to%20her%2C%20one%20reason%20for%20this%20ethnic%20clash%20in%20Manipur%20is%20one%20of%20identity%20movement%2C%20stepmotherly%20treatment%20of%20the%20hill%20tribes%20and%20denial%20of%20legitimate%20space%20and%20autonomy%20to%20the%20hill%20tribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20explained%20what%20is%20disturbing%20is%20that%20Manipuris%20do%20not%20acknowledge%20the%20discrimination%20against%20the%20tribal%20people%20within%20Manipur%20and%20how%20Meitei%20domination%20was%20resented%20by%20the%20tribals.%20While%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20hill%20people%20in%20North%20East%20India%20have%20all%20attained%20the%20highest%20status%20in%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20that%20of%20states%20starting%20with%20Nagaland%20(1963)%2C%20Meghalaya%20for%20Garo-Jaintia-Khasi%20State%201972%2C%20Sikkim%201975%2C%20Mizoram%20and%20Arunachal%201987%20respectively%20but%20to%20the%20tribals%20of%20Manipur%20were%20denied%20even%20Sixth%C2%A0Schedule%20let%20alone%20Statehood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeitei%20demand%20for%20ST%20status%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20spark%20that%20lit%20the%20fire%20on%20May%203%2C%202023%2C%20was%20the%20Meitei%20demand%20to%20be%20recognised%20as%20an%20ST%20tribe%2C%20a%20demand%20strongly%20opposed%20by%20the%20tribals%20of%20Manipur.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20just%20a%20dip%20of%20the%20iceberg.%20The%20root%20cause%2C%20as%20the%20author%20has%20rightly%20pointed%20out%2C%20is%20the%20stepmotherly%20treatment%20of%20the%20hill%20people%20for%20years%20by%20the%20state%20government%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exponential%20growth%20of%20certain%20communities%20which%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20demographic%20engineering%20compounded%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20back%20as%202010%2C%20assistant%20professor%20Sekholal%20Kom%20wrote%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9C%5BT%5Dhe%20Meitei%20identity%20mobilisation%20in%20the%20process%20seems%20to%20have%20excluded%20other%20communities%20from%20the%20Hills%E2%80%A6%20The%20result%20has%20been%20cycles%20of%20mobilisation%20and%20counter-mobilisation%2C%20which%20eventually%20turn%20into%20conflictual%20politics%20posing%20serious%20deterrence%20to%20government%20%E2%80%A6%20In%20short%2C%20much%20of%20the%20politics%20centres%20on%20the%20question%20of%20preserving%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20identity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20recalled%20that%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20was%20inclined%20to%20extend%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20to%20the%20Hill%20Tribes%20of%20Manipur%20as%20the%20state%20government%20had%20recommended%20on%20April%207%2C%202001.%20Since%20the%20state%20government%20had%20failed%20to%20implement%20the%20Sixth%C2%A0Schedule%2C%20the%20ATSUM%20had%20even%20gone%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20demanding%20that%20tribal%20areas%20be%20declared%20as%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2014%2C%202023%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20made%20a%20shocking%20revelation%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cproposal%20on%20the%20inclusion%20of%20the%20Meitei%20Community%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20list%20has%20been%20examined%20and%20rejected%20twice%20over%20the%20last%20four%20decades%2C%20according%20to%20the%20documents%20seen%20by%20the%20Hindu%3B%20once%2C%20in%201982%2C%20by%20the%20Registrar%20General%20of%20India%3B%20and%20again%2C%20in%202001%2C%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20Manipur.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20also%20examined%20the%20conflict%20and%20learnt%20that%20%E2%80%9Cfrom%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20violent%20in%20Manipur%2C%20churches%20were%20a%20prime%20target%20of%20the%20mobs%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20She%20highlighted%20that%20churches%20have%20never%20been%20attacked%20in%20this%20scale%20during%20the%20past%20conflicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVandalising%20and%20burning%20of%20churches%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20With%20the%20escalation%20of%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20churches%20Archbishop%20Dominic%20Lumon%20stated%20on%20June%2015%2C%202023%3A%20%E2%80%9CEach%20of%20the%20over%20200%20Kuki%20villages%20attacked%20had%20either%20one%20or%20multiple%20churches%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20number%20of%20Christian%20denominations%E2%80%A6%20About%20249%20churches%20belonging%20to%20the%20Meitei%20Christians%20have%20been%20destroyed.%20All%20these%20destructions%20took%20place%20with%20precision%20within%2036%20hours%20of%20the%20start%20of%20the%20violence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFree%20movement%20regime%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20demand%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Manipur%20for%20suspension%20of%20Free%20Movement%20Regime%20(FMR)%2C%20%E2%80%9Cunder%20which%20every%20member%20of%20the%20hill%20tribes%2C%20who%20was%20either%20a%20citizen%20of%20India%20or%20of%20Myanmar%20and%20who%20was%20a%20resident%20of%20any%20area%20within%20sixteen%20kilometres%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20Indo-Myanmar%20Border%20(IMB)%2C%20could%20go%20across%20with%20a%20border%20pass%20issued%20by%20a%20competent%20authority%20and%20stay%20for%20up%20to%20two%20weeks%20per%20visits%E2%80%9D%2C%20has%20been%20opposed%20by%20the%20state%20government%20of%20Mizoram%20and%20Nagaland.%20As%20the%20Mizo%20people%20and%20Naga%20people%20are%20trans-border%20tribe%20and%20the%20suspension%20of%20FMR%20will%20amount%20to%20the%20tearing%20apart%20of%20family%20and%20tribes%2C%20they%20naturally%20opposed%20the%20alleged%20suspension%20of%20FMR.%20This%20FMR%20was%20initiated%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20in%202018%2C%20however%2C%20Manipur%20suspended%20the%20FMR%20in%202020%20due%20to%20the%20Covid%20pandemic.%20And%20gradually%20the%20State%20Government%20wishes%20to%20fence%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWar%20on%20drugs%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20the%20Manipur%20government%20campaigned%20for%20war%20on%20drugs%20in%20Manipur%2C%20over%202%2C858%20acres%20of%20poppy%20cultivation%20were%20destroyed.%20The%20author%20asks%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20is%20it%20that%20the%20destruction%20of%20hundreds%20of%20poppy%20fields%20in%20the%20hills%20of%20Ukhrul%2C%20Senapati%2C%20Kangpokpi%2C%20Kamjong%2C%20Churachandpur%20and%20Tengnoupal%20districts%20has%20not%20solved%20the%20problem%3F%E2%80%9D%20She%20went%20on%20to%20question%20the%20state%20government%20for%20covering%20up%20the%20cases%20raised%20by%20state%20cop%20Thounaojam%20Brinda%20on%20the%20arrest%20of%20Lhukhosei%20Zou%2C%20who%20was%20caught%20with%20%E2%80%9C4.595%20kg%20of%20heroin%2C%20280%2C200%20WY%20tablets%2C%20Rs.%2057.18%20lakh%20in%20cash%2C%20another%20Rs.%2095%2C000%20in%20demonetized%20currency%20notes%20and%20several%20other%20incriminating%20articles%E2%80%9D%3Cem%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20but%20was%20eventually%20set%20free%20by%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20124144%2FF1SovOrXoAA5F5U.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20124144%2FF1SovOrXoAA5F5U.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20124144%2FF1SovOrXoAA5F5U-300x147.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20124144%2FF1SovOrXoAA5F5U-1024x501.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664089%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22587%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EManipur%20chief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40NBirenSingh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPoverty%20and%20poppies%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Manipur%20is%20ranked%20the%20third%20poorest%20state%20in%20India%20with%2036.89%25%20of%20its%20people%20living%20below%20the%20poverty%20line%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20author%20revealed%20through%20her%20experience%20in%20the%20state%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpoverty%2C%20food%20insecurity%2C%20and%20material%20needs%20are%20the%20drivers%20of%20illegal%20opium%20production%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%9D.%20The%20price%20of%201%20kg%20of%20opium%20in%20the%20local%20market%20usually%20ranges%20from%20Rs%2050%2C000-70000%20per%20kgs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELooting%20of%20arms%20and%20ammunition%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20author%20remarked%20that%20%E2%80%9Cas%20of%20September%2014%2C%20of%20the%205%2C668%20arms%20that%20had%20been%20stolen%20from%20police%20armouries%2C%201%2C329%20had%20been%20recovered.%20In%20addition%2C%205%2C172%20cases%20of%20arson%20had%20been%20reported%20in%20the%20course%20of%20the%20violence%3Cem%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3EThis%20included%20254%20churches%20and%20132%20temples.%20Of%20the%20thousands%20of%20structures%20set%20on%20fire%2C%204%2C786%20were%20people%E2%80%99s%20homes%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20three-member%20fact-finding%20team%20comprising%20National%20Federation%20of%20Indian%20Women%20(NFIW)%20general%20secretary%20Annie%20Raja%2C%20national%20secretary%20Nisha%20Siddhu%2C%20and%20Delhi-based%20lawyer%20Deeksha%20Dwivedi%20that%20visited%20Manipur%20from%20June%2028%20to%20July%201%2C%202023%2C%20concluded%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cstate-sponsored%20violence%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20government%20continuing%20its%20provocative%20actions.%20Annie%20Raja%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20happening%20in%20Manipur%20is%20not%20communal%20violence%2C%20nor%20is%20it%20merely%20a%20fight%20between%20two%20communities.%20It%20involves%20the%20question%20of%20land%2C%20resources%2C%20and%20the%20presence%20of%20fanatics%20and%20militants.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20author%20is%20of%20the%20view%20that%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20sections%20of%20the%20mainstream%20policy%20and%20media%20community%20outside%20Manipur%E2%80%99%20consider%20this%20clash%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%98petty%20brawl%20between%20two%20ethnic%20groups%20in%20the%20remote%20north-east%20that%20can%20be%20resolved%20only%20if%20both%20sides%20make%20some%20concessions%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20The%20majority%20ignore%20the%20power%20conflict%20between%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20which%20is%20an%20identity%20conflict.%20She%20went%20on%20to%20comment%20that%20the%20problem%20arises%20because%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20former%20%5BMeitei%5D%20enjoys%20greater%20agency%20in%20decision-making%20and%20discourse-setting%20processes%20over%20the%20latter%E2%80%9D.%20She%20even%20went%20on%20to%20question%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20silence%20over%20the%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%20and%20the%20veracity%20as%20to%20why%20the%20Union%20government%20ignored%20to%20implement%20even%20a%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecurity%20forces%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20assertion%20by%20the%20security%20forces%20is%20that%20%E2%80%9Cany%20violence%20in%20the%20country%20can%20be%20dealt%20with%20within%20twenty-four%20to%20forty-eight%20hours%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20this%20round%20of%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20continued%20for%20months%20without%20signs%20of%20abating%20shows%20state%20complicity%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0The%20author%20expressed%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20police%20force%20is%20one%20of%20the%20weakest%20in%20the%20world.%20India%E2%80%99s%20police-to-population%20ratio%20lags%20behind%20most%20countries%20and%20the%20United%20Nations-recommended%20ratio%20of%20one%20police%20personnel%20to%20220%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20case%20of%20violence%20that%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20state%2C%20even%20though%20Manipur%20has%20thousands%20of%20police%20forces%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdeployment%20in%20such%20great%20numbers%20seemed%20to%20have%20little%20effect%20on%20the%20rioting%E2%80%9D.%20Ajai%20Sahni%2C%20founding%20member%20and%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Institute%20of%20Conflict%20Management%2C%20said%20in%20one%20of%20his%20interviews%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20July%202023%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Creason%20for%20the%20prolonged%20violence%20was%20neither%20incompetence%20nor%20lack%20of%20planning%20but%20a%20collusion%20of%20the%20state%3A%20the%20state%20is%20either%20supporting%20or%20orchestrating%20the%20violence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERole%20of%20the%20armed%20forces%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%20The%20author%20writes%20about%20how%20the%20armed%20forces%20in%20collusion%20with%20the%20Kukis%20were%20used%20during%20the%20Naga%20insurgency%20in%20the%20past.%20Home%20Raikhan%2C%20a%20retired%20IRS%20officer%20wrote%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Sangai%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9CKukis%20were%20being%20trained%20and%20supplied%20with%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20at%20Leimakhong%2C%20Manipur%20and%20Zakhama%2C%20Nagaland.%E2%80%99%20Although%20Assam%20Rifle%2C%20the%20oldest%20paramilitary%20force%20in%20India%2C%20%E2%80%98is%20the%20leading%20counter-insurgency%20force%20in%20the%20North-East%E2%80%9D%2C%20resentment%20by%20the%20Meiteis%20against%20the%20Armed%20Force%20dates%20many%20years%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20June%202023%2C%20a%20retired%20high-ranking%20Army%20officer%20tweeted%20about%20the%20dire%20state%20of%20affairs%20in%20the%20state.%20Lt%20Gen%20(retd.)%20L.%20Nishikanta%20Singh%20tweeted%3A%C2%A0%20I%20am%20just%20an%20ordinary%20Indian%20from%20Manipur%20living%20a%20retired%20life.%20The%20state%20is%20now%20Stateless.%20Life%20and%20property%20can%20be%20destroyed%20anytime%20by%20anyone%2C%20just%20like%20in%20Libya%2C%20Lebanon%2C%20Nigeria%2C%20Syria%20etc.%20To%20this%2C%20former%20Army%20chief%20General%20V.P%20Malik%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%98An%20extraordinary%20sad%20call%20from%20a%20retired%20Lt%20General%20from%20Manipur.%20Law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20needs%20urgent%20attention%20at%20the%20highest%20level.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20author%20expressed%20that%20%E2%80%9Canalysing%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20state%20still%20does%20not%20answer%20the%20question%3A%20who%20will%20benefit%20from%20this%20violence%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDemand%20for%20Kuki%20homeland%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20According%20to%20the%20author%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdemand%20for%20a%20Kuki%20homeland%20is%20the%20most%20contentious%20issue%20in%20Manipur%20and%20many%20believe%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20the%20violence%20in%202023%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDevelopment%20funds%20and%20autonomy%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CA%20letter%20written%20by%20L.K.%20Advani%2C%20the%20then%20Deputy%20Home%20Minister%2C%20to%20Chief%20Minister%20Ibobi%20Singh%20reveals%20the%20politics%20of%20manipulation%20which%20has%20deprived%20the%20people%20of%20Hill%20areas%20of%20development.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTribal%20leader%20continually%20complains%20and%20point%20towards%20the%20lack%20of%20infrastructural%20development%2C%20the%20poor%20condition%20of%20the%20education%20and%20health%20services%2C%20endemic%20poverty%2C%20lack%20of%20employment%20opportunities%2C%20and%20of%20access%20to%20resources%20for%20their%20development.%20A%20survey%20of%20budget%20allocation%20for%20the%20hill%20districts%20in%202004-05%20is%20indicative%20%5Bof%5D%20this%20situation%3A%20in%20education%20only%2026%20per%20cent%20was%20allocated%20to%20the%20hill%20districts%2C%20while%20this%20was%2025%20per%20cent%20in%20health%20and%2022%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20public%20works%20department.%20Four%20out%20of%20five%20hill%20districts%20figure%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20heap%20on%20the%20human%20development%20index.%20These%20districts%20also%20have%20a%20larger%20proportion%20of%20the%20poor%20than%20the%20valley%20areas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInsurgency%20and%20identity%20politics%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Way%20back%20in%201981%2C%20Nibeon%20Biswas%2C%20the%20youngest%20son%20of%20the%20late%20Nirod%20Kumar%20Biswas%2C%20the%20bishop%20of%20Assam%2C%20writing%20under%20the%20name%2C%20Nirmal%20Nibedon%2C%20published%20a%20book%20titled%20%3Cem%3ENortheast%20India%3A%20The%20Ethnic%20Explosion%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20his%20preface%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20an%20ethnic%20explosion.%20Make%20no%20mistake%20about%20it.%20Have%20no%20doubts%20about%20it.%20World%20governments%2C%20more%20so%20India%20Southeast%20Asian%20countries%2C%20will%20habe%20to%20closely%20study%20the%20case%20of%20the%20ethnic%20minorities%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20Kachins%20and%20Karens%20of%20Burma%2C%20the%20Mizos%20of%20the%20Ahoms%20of%20India.%20The%20ethnic%20minorities%20of%20India%2C%20particularly%20those%20of%20the%20Mongoloid%20stock%2C%20will%20deserve%20more%20attention.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20It%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20long%20war%20for%20all%20sides%2C%20frighteningly%20effective%20and%20cripplingly%20expensive%20for%20both.%20None%20may%20emerge%20victorious.%20Both%20may%20be%20losers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIdentity%20politics%20has%20deprived%20Manipur%20of%20people%20who%20can%20speak%20for%20the%20entire%20state%2C%20which%20now%20stands%20deeply%20and%20tragically%20divided.%20But%20the%20question%20that%20still%20needs%20an%20answer%20is%3A%20how%20did%20things%20come%20to%20such%20a%20pass%3F%20Who%20was%20really%20behind%20this%20violence%20in%20Manipur%3F%20And%20what%20did%20they%20want%20to%20achieve%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENewly%20unrecognised%20village%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20a%20large%20number%20of%20new%20villages%20which%20have%20sprung%20up%20in%20the%20Kuki-dominated%20districts%20of%20Manipur.%20At%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20June%202022%2C%20leaders%20of%20the%20Co-ordinating%20Committee%20on%20Manipur%20Integrity%20(COCOMI)%20and%20United%20Naga%20Council%20(UNC)%20held%20a%20joint%20media%20conference%20to%20express%20their%20concern%20over%20the%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20new%20villages%20in%20Chandel%2C%20Tengnoupal%2C%20Kangpokpi%2C%20Churachandpur%20and%20Pherzawl%20districts.%20Their%20district%20wise%20break%20up%20of%20unrecognized%20villages%20was%20as%20follows%3A%20Chandel%20(205)%2C%20Tengnoupal%20(130)%2C%20Kangpokpi%20(304)%2C%20Churachandpur%20(281)%20and%20Pherzawl%20(14).%20In%20all%2C%20there%20were%20934%20new%20villages.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbroad-consensus-in-manipur-that-state-responsible-for-ethnic-violence%5C%22%3EManipur%3A%20Both%20Centre%20and%20State%20Played%20a%20Principal%20Role%20in%20Ethnic%20Violence%2C%20Claims%20Fact-Finding%20Team%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20is%20closed%20by%20flagging%20many%20uncomfortable%20questions.%20She%20has%20also%20volunteered%20some%20sensible%20solutions%3A%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20more%20inclusive%20politics.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20cannot%20be%20peace%20without%20justice.%20And%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20justice%20is%20to%20bring%20those%20who%20are%20guilty%20to%20account.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20remarked%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Meiteis%20will%20have%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20they%20have%20dominated%20state%20politics%20and%20the%20people%20in%20the%20Hills%20have%20been%20discriminated%20against%20in%20all%20fields%3A%20economic%2C%20political%20and%20cultural.%E2%80%9D%20To%20the%20Naga%20people%2C%20the%20current%20ethnic%20conflict%20of%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20appears%20ironic.%20Both%20the%20parties%20are%20fighting%20over%20land%20that%20traditionally%20belongs%20to%20the%20Naga%20people.%20She%20concludes%20by%20writing%20that%20%E2%80%9CA%20politics%20which%20encourages%20demographic%20engineering%2C%20which%20is%20rooted%20in%20divide%20and%20rule%2C%20and%20which%20is%20dependent%20on%20conflict%20and%20feeds%20on%20divisions%20must%20be%20eschewed.%20There%20is%20a%20need%20for%20a%20more%20inclusive%20politics%3B%20a%20socio-economic%20programme%20which%20ensures%20economic%20prosperity%20for%20all%20sections%20of%20people%3B%20and%20a%20vision%20that%20celebrates%20cultural%20diversity%2C%20language%20and%20histories.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20warring%20parties%E2%80%94the%20Meiteis%20and%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20people%20could%20not%20see%20eye%20to%20eye%20it%20is%20for%20the%20third%20party%E2%80%94the%20Naga%20people%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Central%20government%20to%20play%20an%20honest%20peace-broker%20in%20order%20to%20bring%20reconciliation%2C%20find%20a%20solution%2C%20and%20urgently%20restore%20peace%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20has%20been%20highly%20appreciated%20by%20the%20Imasi%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20sum%2C%20the%20book%20%3Cem%3EShooting%20the%20Sun%3C%2Fem%3E%20ought%20to%20be%20read%20by%20decision-makers%2C%20policy-makers%2C%20and%20all%20the%20stakeholders.%20I%20have%20no%20hesitation%20in%20recommending%20this%20book%2C%20a%20must-read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ERam%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EMuivah%20is%20a%20member%20of%20legislative%20assembly%20(MLA)%20from%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Ukhrul.%20He%20retired%20from%20the%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705327357000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04085450%2FFvO7YL1aEAAlR43.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fin-search-of-answers-for-the-manipur-violence-a-new-book-takes-a-deep-dive-into-the-conflict%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nandita%20Haksar's%20latest%20book%20'Shooting%20the%20Sun'%20goes%20into%20a%20multitude%20of%20issues%20with%20meticulous%20research%20to%20explain%20the%20conflict%20and%20the%20government's%20response%20to%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fin-search-of-answers-for-the-manipur-violence-a-new-book-takes-a-deep-dive-into-the-conflict%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Barbara%20Corcoran%20says%20all%20great%20entrepreneurs%20have%20imposter%20syndrome%2C%20and%20it's%20key%20to%20success%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222329%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Barbara%20Corcoran%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a5265adcdb354a98578ad0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221747%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBarbara%20Corcoran%20founded%20The%20Corcoran%20Group%20and%20is%20a%20%26quot%3BShark%20Tank%26quot%3B%20investor.%20%3Cp%3EMichael%20Kovac%20%2F%20Contributor%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBarbara%20Corcoran%20said%20having%20imposter%20syndrome%20or%20self-doubt%20at%20work%20is%20beneficial.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20is%20because%20it%20drives%20people%20to%20work%20harder%2C%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECorcoran%2C%20who%20founded%C2%A0real%20estate%20brokerage%20The%20Corcoran%20Group%2C%20said%20her%20success%20is%20due%20to%20her%20insecurity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShark%20Tank%26quot%3B%20investor%20Barbara%20Corcoran%20said%20there%20are%20benefits%20to%20feeling%20a%20little%20insecure%20at%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20let%20you%20in%20on%20a%20little%20secret%3A%20all%20great%20entrepreneurs%20have%20imposter%20syndrome%2C%26quot%3B%20Corcoran%20wrote%20in%20the%20caption%20below%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40barbara.corcoran%2Fvideo%2F7320307538954865966%3Fis_from_webapp%3D1%26sender_device%3Dpc%26web_id%3D7156168240485582341%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eone%20of%20her%20recent%20TikTok%20videos%3C%2Fu%3E%