ww.businessinsider.com%2Fchristian-nationalism-distorts-american-and-christian-values-group-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EChristian%20nationalism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Eauthoritarianism%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3Eand%20democracy%20for%20your%20latest%20book%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20book%20responds%20to%20a%20crisis%20that%20I%20see%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20only%20here%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20is%20that%20democracy%20itself%20is%20losing%20support%2C%20either%20explicitly%20or%20implicitly%2C%20and%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20people%20who%20are%20weakening%20their%20support%20of%20democracy%20or%20abandoning%20it%20entirely%20are%20Christians%2C%20and%20they%20were%20motivated%20by%20what%20they%20would%20consider%20to%20be%20Christian%20motivations.%20My%20dissertation%20was%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-nazi-germany-today-world-war-ii-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENazi%20era%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20Holocaust.%20I'm%20a%20strong%20believer%20in%20democracy%2C%20and%20I%20also%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20knowledge%20about%20what%20happens%20when%20democracy%20is%20abandoned%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20good%2C%20so%20I'm%20very%20passionate%20about%20protecting%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20there%20a%20particular%20incident%20or%20flash%20point%20that%20you%20see%20as%20of%20significant%20concern%20about%20the%20challenges%20that%20are%20facing%20democracy%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20the%20immediate%20crisis%20is%20the%20phenomenon%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20the%20strong%20conservative%20Christian%20support%20for%20Trump%2C%20which%20continues%20to%20this%20day.%20It%20went%20to%20a%20whole%20new%20level%20when%20he%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20results%20of%20the%202020%20election%20and%20was%20determined%20not%20to%20leave%20the%20White%20House%2C%20and%20then%20helped%20to%20trigger%20a%20violent%20attack%20on%20the%20Capitol%20Building%20on%20January%206%2C%202021.%20And%20now%20in%20his%20campaign%20for%20the%202024%20election%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-rhetoric-mirroring-nazi-fascism-hitler-expert-warns-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe's%20speaking%20in%20openly%20authoritarian%20ways%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20statements%20are%20even%20more%20alarming%20than%20things%20that%20he%20has%20said%20in%20the%20past.%20So%20you%20have%20a%20uniquely%20dangerous%20politician%20in%20the%20history%20of%20American%20politics%2C%20but%20you%20also%20have%20this%20stubbornly%20loyal%20base%20of%20support%20for%20this%20man%20from%20conservative%20Christians%2C%20and%20that%20is%20what%20I'm%20trying%20to%20explore%20in%20the%20book.%20What's%20the%20secret%3F%20Why%20the%20support%3F%20And%20I%20think%20I've%20got%20it%20pretty%20well%20figured%20out.%20And%20so%20that's%20what%20the%20book%20does%2C%20while%20also%20challenging%20it%20and%20saying%3A%20We%20got%20to%20do%20better%20than%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20tell%20me%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20about%20the%20reasons%20that%20you've%20found%20why%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20such%20a%20significant%20base%20among%20Christian%20conservatives%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20hypothesis%20is%20that%20there's%20a%20reactionary%20dynamic%20on%20the%20part%20of%20many%20morally%20and%20religiously%20traditionalist%20people%2C%20which%20could%20be%20Christians%2C%20Muslims%2C%20or%20Jewish%20people.%20In%20historically%20Christian-dominated%20countries%20like%20the%20US%2C%20the%20basic%20formula%20is%20you%20have%20a%20population%20that%20is%20used%20to%20being%20in%20control%20of%20politics%20and%20culture.%20And%20they're%20losing%20or%20have%20lost%20that%20control%20because%20of%20political%2C%20legal%2C%20and%20cultural%20changes%20over%20many%20decades.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcivil-rights-moments-historic-past-150-years-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultural%20changes%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20have%20happened%20in%20the%20US%20since%20the%201960s%20have%20not%20been%20accepted%20by%20many%20traditional%20Christians.%20These%20would%20be%20things%20like%20legal%20abortion%2C%20legal%20same-sex%20relationships%2C%20the%20feminist%20movement%2C%20and%20the%20sexual%20revolution.%20In%20different%20countries%2C%20it's%20different%20things%2C%20but%20for%20the%20US%2C%20that%20includes%20large-scale%20immigration%20from%20non-European%20countries%20and%2C%20I%20would%20also%20say%2C%20sadly%2C%20the%20significant%20racial%20backlash%20to%20a%20multiracial%20society%20with%20equal%20rights%20for%20people%20of%20color.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20hypothesis%20is%20that%20the%20constant%20liberalizing%20and%20pluralizing%20of%20American%20culture%20has%20evoked%20a%20rather%20fierce%20reaction%20on%20the%20part%20of%20a%20chunk%20of%20the%20population%20that%20you%20could%20put%20at%20maybe%2025%25%2C%20mostly%20conservative%20Catholics%2C%20evangelicals%2C%20fundamentalists%2C%20Pentecostals%2C%20and%20maybe%20some%20people%20of%20other%20religions%20too.%20The%20initial%20strategy%20of%20the%20politically%20active%20reactionaries%20was%20to%20re-evangelize%20the%20country%20through%20church%20work%20and%20then%20to%20partner%20with%20the%20Republican%20Party%20to%20elect%20politicians%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fronald-reagan-uses-racist-language-against-africans-in-released-tape-2019-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERonald%20Reagan%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20would%20advance%20their%20moral%20agenda.%20And%20then%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20the%20evangelicals%2C%20the%20fundamentalists%2C%20and%20so%20on%20would%20support%20Reagan%20and%20the%20Republican%20Party.%20That's%20the%20kind%20of%20traditional%20Christian%20right%20strategy%20that%20goes%20back%20to%20the%2070s.%20My%20assessment%20is%20that%20Trump%2C%20in%20one%20sense%2C%20was%20just%20the%20latest%20product%20of%20that%20partnership.%20But%20in%20another%20sense%2C%20when%20they%20followed%20him%20right%20over%20the%20cliff%20to%20insurrection%20and%20authoritarianism%2C%20you're%20talking%20about%20an%20entirely%20new%20stage.%20So%20you've%20got%20the%20reactionary%20part%2C%20the%20authoritarian%20part%2C%20which%20is%20resistant%20to%20social%20changes%20that%20they%20don't%20like%20and%20so%20are%20galvanized%20by%20the%20authoritarianism%20of%20a%20man%20like%20Trump%2C%20and%20you%20have%20a%20percentage%20of%20people%20who%20are%20willing%20to%20sacrifice%20democracy%20to%20get%20what%20they%20want%20politically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20what%2C%20from%20your%20perspective%2C%20would%20that%20look%20like%20if%20that's%20the%20sacrifice%20that's%20being%20made%3F%20What%20are%20the%20potential%20consequences%20there%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20have%20meant%20that%20if%20Trump%20had%20managed%20to%20pull%20off%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fofficial-if-trump-marched-capitol-january-6-been-an-insurrection-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoup%20on%20January%206%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20had%20managed%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20White%20House%20despite%20losing%20the%20election%2C%20they%20would%20have%20supported%20him.%20If%20Trump%20were%20to%20get%20elected%20again%20and%20propose%20abolishing%20the%20two-term%20limit%2C%20they%20would%20support%20that%2C%20too.%20It%20could%20also%20look%20like%20repudiating%20the%20First%20Amendment%2C%20which%20guarantees%20religious%20liberty%20and%20disestablishment%20of%20religion%2C%20and%20saying%2C%20'No%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20officially%20enshrine%20Christian%20values%20into%20the%20Constitution.'%20It%20could%20include%20weakening%20the%20independence%20of%20the%20judiciary%2C%20throwing%20political%20opponents%20in%20jail%2C%20weakening%20all%20available%20checks%20and%20balances%20to%20the%20government%2C%20or%20intimidating%20the%20media%20so%20that%20you%20wouldn't%20have%20honest%2C%20critical%20reporting%20of%20what%20was%20going%20on.%20And%20in%20the%20book%20I%20talked%20about%20various%20strategies%20that%20have%20been%20tried%20in%20different%20countries.%20I%20also%20point%20out%20that%20there%20are%20these%20conservative%20Christian%20scholars%20who%20are%20so%20disillusioned%20about%20the%20results%20of%20democracy%20as%20we%20have%20it%20in%20this%20country%20that%20they%20also%20are%20supportive%20of%20a%20serious%20reconsideration%20of%20how%20we%20do%20democracy%20here.%20And%20they%20might%20favor%20some%20kind%20of%20return%20to%20an%20officially%20Christian%20state%20with%20Christian%20morality%20essentially%20dictated%20by%20law%20and%20Christianity%20being%20enshrined%20legally%20and%20in%20culture%20as%20the%20official%20source%20of%20the%20laws%20and%20values%20of%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20mention%20that%20there%20might%20be%20roughly%20about%2025%25%20of%20the%20population%20that's%20really%20kind%20of%20reactionary%20and%20committed%20to%20this%20authoritarian%20ideology.%20Since%20they're%20not%20a%20majority%2C%20how%20much%20damage%20could%20they%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thing%20about%20radical%20politics%20is%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20have%2051%25%20for%20a%20radical%20political%20strategy%20to%20prevail%20in%20a%20country.%20What%20you%20need%20is%20a%20significantly%20committed%20minority%20and%20then%20enough%20other%20people%20who%20are%20either%20intimidated%20or%20who%20are%20simply%20willing%20to%20go%20along%20because%20they%20don't%20quite%20see%20what%20is%20at%20stake%20or%2C%20on%20the%20whole%2C%20they%20prefer%20authoritarian%20politics%2C%20which%20has%20results%20that%20they%20might%20go%20for%20instead%20of%20democracy%2C%20which%20has%20results%20that%20they%20don't%20like.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESo%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20hav