system%20seeing%20how%20this%20extremist%20ideology%20has%20co-opted%20this%20religious%20population%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20some%20years%20ago%20that%20American%20fundamentalist%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falexandria-ocasio-cortez-antisemitic-christian-fundamentalism-israel-palestinian-conflict-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevangelical%20Christianity%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20not%20my%20home.%20I%20did%20identify%20as%20an%20evangelical%20Christian%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20but%20I'm%20glad%20that%20I%20have%20left.%20There's%20something%20really%20toxic%20there.%20But%20that%20doesn't%20rattle%20my%20faith%20in%20that%20my%20faith%20in%20Jesus%20is%20not%20related%20to%20the%20malformed%20monstrosity%20that%20has%20emerged%20since%2C%20say%2C%202015.%20I%20understand%20it%20to%20be%20an%20aberration%20and%20a%20disastrous%20one.%20And%20I%20know%20lots%20and%20lots%20and%20lots%20of%20Christian%20people%20who%20also%20know%20it%20to%20be%20a%20disaster%20and%20who%20have%20rejected%20it%20utterly.%20I%20used%20to%20say%20to%20my%20students%3A%20there's%20no%20one%20version%20of%20Christianity%2C%20there's%20many%20versions.%20This%20is%20just%20a%20particularly%20disastrous%20one.%20It%20just%20needs%20to%20be%20called%20out%20for%20what%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20are%20you%20hopeful%20in%20our%20ability%20to%20overcome%20this%20disaster%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20back%20to%20the%20political%20side%2C%20let's%20say%20the%20question%20is%3A%20will%20our%20democracy%20survive%3F%20We%20have%20strengths%20in%20our%20political%20system%20built%20in%20over%20240%20years%2C%20that%20are%20not%20easy%20to%20be%20overturned.%20A%20free%20press%2C%20separation%20of%20powers%2C%20the%20military%20not%20being%20involved%20in%20politics%2C%20an%20independent%20judiciary%2C%20watchdog%20groups%2C%20and%20the%20civil%20society%20we%20have.%20We%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20str