just%20two%20hours%20away%20in%20Varanasi.%20The%20farmers%20are%2C%20in%20general%2C%20unhappy%20with%20the%20land%20acquisition%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flittle-known-about-mughal-era-mosque-in-up-where-muslim-youth-was-booked-for-offering-azaan%5C%22%3ELittle%20Known%20About%20Mughal-Era%20%E2%80%98Mosque%E2%80%99%20in%20UP%20Where%20Muslim%20Youth%20Was%20Booked%20for%20Offering%20Azaan%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E6.%20The%20farmers%20in%20Hardoi%2C%20Unnao%2C%20Sitapur%20and%20most%20of%20U.P.%20have%20to%20keep%20awake%20all%20night%20to%20save%20their%20crops%20from%20stray%20cattle.%20The%20government%20claims%20to%20provide%20Rs.%2050%20per%20cattle%20per%20day%20to%20feed%20them%20but%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20dedicated%20budget%20to%20build%20cow%20sheds.%20Hence%2C%20most%20gram%20pradhans%2C%20like%20the%20one%20from%20Gram%20Sabha%20Mahua%20Danda%20in%20Hardoi%20District%20try%20to%20shirk%20their%20responsibility.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20the%20local%20Sandila%20MLA%2C%20belonging%20to%20his%20own%20caste%2C%20is%20supporting%20him%20against%20the%20directives%20of%20the%20chief%20secretary%20to%20put%20all%20stray%20cattle%20in%20cow%20sheds%20and%20%3Cem%3Egaushalas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Meanwhile%2C%20farmers%20suffer%20and%20some%20have%20even%20given%20up%20agriculture%20as%20the%20UP%20government%20has%20made%20it%20illegal%20to%20fence%20their%20fields%20with%20bladed%20wires.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E7.%20The%20BJP%20government%20has%20also%20come%20up%20with%20an%20ingenious%20way%20of%20avoiding%20increase%20in%20Urea%20fertiliser%E2%80%99s%20rates.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Ffertiliser-minister-says-neem-coated-urea-available-at-rs-266-5%2F45-kg-bag-asks-sp-prez-not-to-mislead-farmers%2Farticleshow%2F106727977.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%20They%20have%20simply%20reduced%20the%20quantity%20of%20Urea%20in%20a%20bag%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%2050%20kg%20to%2040%20kg%2C%20in%20two%20instalments%2C%20without%20changing%20the%20price.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E8.%20The%20Gram%20Sabha%20of%20Aseni%20in%20Barabanki%20passed%20a%20resolution%20against%20liquor%20shops%20in%20the%20village%20in%202021.%20However%2C%20district%20officials%20said%20it%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20state%20policy%20and%20lathi-charged%20a%20demonstration%20demanding%20their%20closure.%20Under%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20rule%2C%20foreign%20liquor%20shops%20are%20doing%20brisk%20business.%20However%2C%20liquor%20shops%20have%20been%20ordered%20shut%20only%20for%20January%2022%2C%20exposing%20the%20hypocrisy%20of%20the%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E9.%20All%20contractual%20employees%20like%20para-teachers%20are%20agitating%20against%20the%20government%20for%20regularisation%20of%20their%20jobs%20or%20at%20least%20an%20increase%20in%20their%20modest%20honoraria.%20Just%20before%20the%20last%20assembly%20election%20in%20UP%20in%202022%2C%20an%20aspirant%20for%20a%20government%20teaching%20post%2C%20Shikha%20Pal%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ahmedabadmirror.com%2Fjob-seeker-has-been-sitting-atop-water-tank-for-past-120-days%2F81814466.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20sat%20atop%20a%20water%20tank%20at%20the%20education%20directorate%20for%20about%20half%20a%20year%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20protesting%20against%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20recruitment%20policy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E10.%20Additionally%2C%20Rs%2010%20postal%20orders%2C%20which%20are%20required%20to%20file%20an%20application%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%2C%20have%20disappeared%20from%20post%20offices%20across%20UP%20%E2%80%93%20Lucknow%2C%20Kanpur%2C%20Barabanki%2C%20Moradabad%20and%20Varanasi%20%E2%80%93%20so%20that%20people%20cannot%20hold%20the%20government%20accountable%20by%20asking%20uncomfortable%20questions.%20This%20is%20symbolic%20of%20suppression%20of%20all%20dissent%20in%20BJP%20rule.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20clear%20that%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20not%20going%20to%20bring%20Ram%20Rajya%20in%20UP%20or%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%20At%20best%2C%20it%E2%80%99ll%20help%20ensure%20a%20political%20victory%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20that%20is%20the%20reason%20the%20consecration%20is%20happening%20even%20before%20the%20construction%20is%20complete.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20a%20religious%20temple.%20It%20is%20a%20political%20temple.%20It%20is%20a%20project%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20organisations%20which%20has%20succeeded%20because%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20power.%20Some%20of%20the%20opposition%20parties%20are%20unsure%20how%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20invitation%20for%20the%20consecration.%20They%20should%20outrightly%20reject%20it%20as%20it%20is%20a%20BJP%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%20event.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20must%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20Hindutva%20organisations%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20Hindu%20religion.%20No%20senior%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20Jan%20Sangh%2C%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20or%20BJP%20leader%20has%20ever%20written%20a%20book%20on%20Hindu%20religion%20like%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20Vinoba%20Bhave%2C%20Sarvapalli%20Radhakrishnan%2C%20Aurobindo%20Ghosh%2C%20etc%2C%20have%20done.%20Hence%2C%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20feel%20guilty%20about%20not%20being%20part%20of%20the%20consecration%20ceremony.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20voters%20need%20to%20distinguish%20between%20Hindu%20religion%20and%20the%20politics%20of%20Hindutva.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESandeep%20Pandey%20is%20the%20General%20Secretary%20of%20Socialist%20Party%20(India).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705325299000%2C%22visual%22%3A%