ummary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106869735.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EDarsheel%20Safary%20reunites%20with%20Tisca%20Chopra%20at%20Ira%20Khan's%20wedding%20reception.%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%2C%20Salman%20Khan%2C%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%2C%20Katrina%20Kaif%2C%20Rekha%20attend.%20Darsheel%20Safary%20appreciates%20'Taare%20Zameen%20Par'%20recognition.%20He%20has%20upcoming%20projects%20with%20Vinay%20Bhardwaj%2C%20Hritik%20Sanghavi%2C%20and%20Atul%20Garg.%20Tisca%20Chopra%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20'Dahan%20%E2%80%93%20Raakan%20ka%20Rahasya'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Food%2C%20Restless%20Children%26quot%3B%3A%20Fliers%20Claim%20Harrowing%20Air%20India%20Flight%20Delay%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20passenger%20of%20an%20Air%20India%20plane%20who%20remained%20stuck%20inside%20the%20aircraft%20for%20six%20hours%20has%20pointed%20to%20several%20factors%20that%20sparked%20anger%20among%20people%2C%20after%20several%20airlines%20cancelled%20hundreds%20of%20fights%20due%20to%20low%20visibility%20in%20Delhi%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20passenger%2C%20seen%20in%20a%20viral%20video%20of%20him%20slapping%20an%20IndiGo%20pilot%2C%20has%20been%20arrested%2C%20the%20police%20said.%20The%20passenger%2C%20Sahil%20Kataria%2C%20was%20released%20on%20bail%20later.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERifka%20Verma%2C%20the%20Air%20India%20passenger%2C%20told%20NDTV%20today%20their%20patience%20ran%20thin%20due%20to%20a%20combination%20of%20factors%20-%20children%20getting%20restless%2C%20not%20getting%20food%2C%20and%20air-conditioning%20not%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20flight%20was%20to%20take-off%20at%209%20am.%20It%20was%20obvious%20seeing%20the%20weather%20condition%20it%20would%20be%20delayed.%20But%20they%20kept%20giving%20conflicting%20information.%20After%202%20pm%2C%20when%20the%20aircraft%20was%20ready%2C%20they%20said%20they%20don't%20have%20a%20crew%20as%20that%20crew%20has%20been%20put%20on%20another%20flight%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Verma%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20absolute%20chaos.%20After%20they%20got%20a%20crew%20it%20was%205.30%20pm.%20We%20boarded%20around%208%20pm.%20There%20was%20no%20pilot.%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20ground%20staff%20or%20the%20crew%20is%20to%20blame.%20It's%20the%20management%2C%20or%20rather%20mismanagement...%20There%20was%20no%20food%2C%20only%20some%20packets%20of%20chips%20in%2017%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20not%20valuing%20their%20customers%2C%20and%20not%20keeping%20them%20informed%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Verma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmooth%20coordination%20in%20Delhi%20airport%20broke%20down%20yesterday%20after%20hundreds%20of%20passengers%20of%20delayed%20flights%20demanded%20answers%20from%20the%20airlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stressful%20day%20also%20saw%20the%20passenger%20of%20an%20IndiGo%20flight%20attacking%20a%20pilot%20inside%20the%20plane%20while%20it%20was%20on%20the%20tarmac.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India%20in%20a%20statement%20today%20said%20it%20regrets%20the%20disruption%20to%20operations%20arising%20from%20the%20last%20few%20days'%20dense%20fog%20in%20north%20India%2C%20including%20at%20%26quot%3Bour%20main%20Delhi%20hub%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20some%20diversions%20and%20desynchronisation%20of%20aircraft%20and%20crew%20rotations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20working%20hard%20to%20restore%20schedules%2C%20and%20sincerely%20regret%20the%20inconvenience%20caused%20to%20our%20passengers%2C%26quot%3B%20Air%20India%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECivil%20Aviation%20Minister%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20today%20said%20they%20have%20taken%20steps%20to%20avoid%20similar%20circumstances%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYesterday%2C%20Delhi%20witnessed%20unprecedented%20fog%20wherein%20visibility%20fluctuated%20for%20several%20hours%2C%20and%20at%20times%2C%20dropped%20to%20zero%20between%205%20am%20and%209%20am%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Scindia%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20authorities%2C%20therefore%2C%20were%20compelled%20to%20enforce%20a%20shut-down%20of%20operations%20for%20some%20time%20even%20on%20CAT%20III%20runways%20(CAT%20III%20runways%20cannot%20handle%20zero-visibility%20operations).%20The%20decision%20was%20taken%20keeping%20passenger%20safety%20in%20mind%2C%20which%20remains%20the%20foremost%20priority%20for%20all%20in%20the%20aviation%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Minister%20suggested%20operationalising%20the%20CAT%20III-enabled%20fourth%20runway.%20The%20regulator%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20(DGCA)%20will%20release%20a%20standard%20operating%20procedure%20(SOP)%20aimed%20at%20enhancing%20communication%20and%20passenger%20facilitation%20for%20airlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20measure%20aims%20to%20minimise%20passenger%20discomfort%20caused%20by%20flight%20cancellations%20and%20delays%20attributed%20to%20adverse%20weather%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Scindia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705324740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fei93tab_air-india-flight-horror-650_625x300_15_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fair-india-flight-horror-17-hour-wait-for-delhi-mumbai-passengers-4867405%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20passenger%20of%20an%20Air%20India%20plane%20who%20remained%20stuck%20inside%20the%20aircraft%20for%20six%20hours%20has%20pointed%20to%20several%20factors%20that%20sparked%20anger%20among%20people%2C%20after%20several%20airlines%20cancelled%20hundreds%20of%20fights%20due%20to%20low%20visibility%20in%20Delhi%20yesterday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%