ading%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bnuclear%26quot%3B.%20Betavolt%20has%20managed%20to%20squeeze%2063%20isotopes%20into%20that%20module%20that's%20smaller%20than%20a%20coin%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said%20in%20its%20report.%20The%20company%20said%20it%20is%20the%20first%20battery%20in%20the%20world%20to%20realise%20the%20miniaturisation%20of%20atomic%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next-generation%20battery%20is%20already%20being%20tested%20and%20will%20be%20mass%20produced%20for%20commercial%20applications%20like%20phones%20and%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBetavolt%20atomic%20energy%20batteries%20can%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20long-lasting%20power%20supply%20in%20multiple%20scenarios%2C%20such%20as%20aerospace%2C%20AI%20equipment%2C%20medical%20equipment%2C%20microprocessors%2C%20advanced%20sensors%2C%20small%20drones%20and%20micro-robots%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20new%20energy%20innovation%20will%20help%20China%20gain%20a%20leading%20edge%20in%20the%20new%20round%20of%20the%20AI%20technological%20revolution%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20dimensions%20of%20the%20battery%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20measures%2015%20x%2015%20x%205%20millimetres%20and%20is%20made%20of%20wafer-thin%20layers%20of%20nuclear%20isotopes%20and%20diamond%20semiconductors%2C%20as%20per%20Futurism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nuclear%20battery%20currently%20generates%20100%20microwatts%20of%20power%20at%203%20volts.%20However%2C%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20reach%20a%201-watt%20power%20output%20by%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetavolt%20said%20the%20radiation%20poses%20no%20danger%20to%20the%20human%20body%2C%20making%20it%20usable%20in%20medical%20devices%20such%20as%20pacemakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20the%20battery%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20used%20in%20the%20battery%20taps%20into%20the%20energ