0venture%20capital%20funds%20through%20migration%20to%20the%20AIF%20regime%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Finvestment%2Fsebi-mulls-liquidation-flexibility-for-aif-vcfs-to-deal-with-beyond-tenure-124011500515_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Finvestment%2Fsebi-mulls-liquidation-flexibility-for-aif-vcfs-to-deal-with-beyond-tenure-124011500515_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Finvestment%2Fsebi-mulls-liquidation-flexibility-for-aif-vcfs-to-deal-with-beyond-tenure-124011500515_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPilot%20Blamed%20Us%20Passengers%26quot%3B%3A%20What%20Russian%20Woman%20Said%20On%20Viral%20IndiGo%20Video%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20eyewitness%2C%20who%20recorded%20the%20viral%20video%20of%20an%20IndiGo%20pilot%20being%20physically%20assaulted%20by%20a%20passenger%20on%20board%20the%20aircraft%2C%20has%20revealed%20the%20circumstances%20that%20led%20to%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvgenia%20Belskaia%2C%20a%20Russian%20model%20and%20actress%20based%20in%20India%2C%20was%20onboard%20the%20IndiGo%20flight%20(6E-2175)%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Goa.%20The%20flight%20was%20delayed%20for%2013%20hours%20at%20the%20Delhi%20airport%20yesterday%2C%20which%20led%20to%20a%20furore%20among%20passengers%20against%20the%20crew%20and%20the%20pilots%20over%20the%20long%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEyewitness%20Account%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Belsakaia%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20flying%20her%20team%20to%20Goa%20from%20Delhi%20and%20reached%20the%20airport%20early%20to%20board%20the%20flight%2C%20which%20was%20scheduled%20to%20take%20off%20at%207%3A40%20am.%20The%20IndiGo%20team%20was%20saying%20that%20the%20flight%20had%20been%20delayed%20by%20an%20hour.%20It%20went%20on%20for%20at%20least%2010%20hours%20until%20we%20were%20allowed%20to%20board%20the%20plane.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20boarding%20the%20aircraft%2C%20we%20were%20told%20that%20the%20flight%20had%20been%20delayed%20by%20two%20hours.%20The%20passengers%20were%20angry%20and%20started%20asking%20questions%20from%20the%20crew%20and%20the%20pilot%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20actress%20condemned%20the%20shocking%20act%20of%20physical%20assault%20but%20partly%20blamed%20the%20pilot%20for%20aggravating%20the%20situation.%20%26quot%3BThe%20pilot%20came%20and%20said%20you%20are%20asking%20too%20many%20questions%20and%20we%20missed%20our%20turn%20because%20of%20this.%26quot%3B%20The%20eyewitness%20said%20the%20%26quot%3BPilot%20blamed%20the%20passengers%20for%20the%20delay%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20viral%20video%20recorded%20by%20Ms%20Belsakaia%2C%20a%20man%20in%20a%20yellow%20hoodie%20ran%20up%20from%20the%20last%20row%20and%20hit%20Anup%20Kumar%2C%20the%20flight's%20co-pilot%2C%20who%20was%20announcing%20a%20further%20delay.%20The%20accused%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Sahil%20Kataria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20wrong%20to%20hit%20the%20pilot%2C%20but%20why%20is%20he%20blaming%20the%20passengers%3F%20Everyone%20was%20nervous%20and%20instead%20of%20supporting%20them%20you%20made%20it%20worse%2C%26quot%3B%20Evgenia%20said%20in%20her%20video%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BYou%20Can't%20Do%20This%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20Sahil%20Kataria%2C%20tried%20to%20punch%20the%20co-pilot%2C%20Anup%20Kumar%2C%20and%20the%20cabin%20crew%20rushed%20to%20help%20the%20pilot%20and%20told%20the%20accused%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20do%20this...you%20can't%20do%20this!%26quot%3B.%20To%20this%2C%20Mr%20Kataria%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20can't%20I%20do%20this%3F%20Why%20can't%20I%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChalana%20hai%20to%20chala%2C%20warna%20gate%20khol%26quot%3B%20(fly%20if%20you%20want%20to%2C%20otherwise%20open%20the%20gate)%2C%20the%20accused%20said%20after%20hitting%20Mr%20Kumar.%20The%20pilot%20has%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20him%20and%20the%20airline%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20process%20of%20filing%20an%20official%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flier%20later%20apologised%20to%20the%20pilot%20on%20the%20tarmac%20after%20he%20deboarded%20from%20the%20plane%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSir%2C%20I%20am%20sorry%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20which%20the%20pilot%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20sorry%2C%20you%20raised%20hands%20on%20me%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Are%20The%20Protocols%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findigo-passenger-slaps-pilot-sahil-kataria-delhi-goa-flight-man-who-slapped-indigo-pilot-was-sitting-in-plane-for-several-hours-4866520%5C%22%3ECommercial%20aviation%20protocols%3C%2Fa%3E%20state%20that%20departure%20slots%20will%20only%20be%20assigned%20once%20the%20plane's%20doors%20are%20shut%20and%20the%20sooner%20they%20are%20locked%20the%20quicker%20each%20plane%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20depart.%20This%20is%20why%20airlines%20sometimes%20board%20earlier%20than%20indicated%20on%20their%20schedules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20according%20to%20aviation%20protocols%2C%20once%20a%20plane's%20doors%20are%20shut%20the%20passengers%20may%20not%20leave%20the%20flight.%20There%20are%20multiple%20reasons%20for%20this%2C%20including%20security.%20Passengers%20who%20disembark%20will%20go%20back%20into%20the%20terminal%20and%20must%20pass%20baggage%20checks%20a%20second%20time%2C%20which%20will%20create%20more%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20case%2C%20it%20was%20not%20and%20the%20earlier%20delays%20-%20caused%20at%20least%20partly%20by%20bad%20weather%20-%20triggered%20a%20further%20delay%20since%20a%20new%20crew%20had%20to%20be%20assigned%20to%20the%20plane.%20According%20to%20FDTL%20norms%2C%20or%20flight%20duty%20time%20limitation%2C%20cabin%20and%20flight%20crews%20can%20only%20work%20a%20fixed%20number%20of%20hours%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnup%20Kumar%2C%20the%20captain%20attacked%20by%20Sahil%20Kataria%2C%20was%20part%20of%20the%20replacement%20crew.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705315860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F8qreego_evgenia-belskaia_625x300_15_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpilot-blamed-us-passengers-what-russian-woman-evgenia-belskaia-said-on-viral-indigo-video-4867063%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20eyewitness%2C%20who%20recorded%20the%20viral%20video%20of%20an%20IndiGo%20pilot%20being%20physically%20assaulted%20by%20a%20passenger%20on%20board%20the%20aircraft%2C%20has%20revealed%20the%20circumstances%20that%20led%20to%20the%20incident.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpilot-blamed-us-passengers-what-russian-woman-evgenia-belskaia-said-on-viral-indigo-video-4867063%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpilot-blamed-us-passengers-what-russian-woman-evgenia-belskaia-said-on-viral-indigo-video-4867063%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpilot-blamed-us-passengers-what-russian-woman-evgenia-belskaia-said-on-viral-indigo-video-4867063%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sensex%20closes%20above%2073k%20for%20the%20first%20time%3B%20Nifty50%20above%2022k%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705315450000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106865074%2Cimgsize-97020.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fstock-market-today-bse-sensex-nifty50-january-15-2024-dalal-street-bombay-stock-exchange-hits-new-high-top-reasons%2Farticleshow%2F106864