22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchalana-hai-toh-chala-what-angry-flier-told-indigo-pilot-after-attacking-him-4865504%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchalana-hai-toh-chala-what-angry-flier-told-indigo-pilot-after-attacking-him-4865504%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchalana-hai-toh-chala-what-angry-flier-told-indigo-pilot-after-attacking-him-4865504%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BVirat%20Kohli%20Will%20Lose...%26quot%3B%3A%20Star%20Batter%20Issued%20Big%20Warning%20On%20T20I%20Return%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Indian%20opener%20Aakash%20Chopra%20expressed%20surprise%20at%20Virat%20Kohli's%20attacking%20approach%20during%20the%20second%20T20I%20between%20India%20and%20Afghanistan%20but%20also%20cautioned%20that%20if%20he%20starts%20playing%20at%20a%20much%20higher%20strike%20rate%2C%20he%20could%20lose%20his%20consistency%2C%20which%20has%20been%20one%20of%20his%20hallmarks.%20Fans%20in%20Indore%20and%20those%20watching%20through%20electronic%20devices%20had%20a%20reason%20to%20rejoice%20as%20'King%20Kohli'%20made%20his%20return%20to%20the%20T20I%20format%20after%20more%20than%20a%20year%20following%20a%20crushing%20loss%20to%20England%20in%20the%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%202022%20semifinal.%20Virat%20put%20aside%20all%20debates%20about%20his%20strike%20rate%20within%20a%20matter%20of%20a%20few%20bat%20swings%2C%20batting%20with%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20well%20above%20150%20and%20often%20dancing%20down%20the%20pitch%20to%20smash%20his%20trademark%20shots.%20There%20were%20no%20signs%20of%20rust%20whatsoever%20as%20he%20entertained%20fans%20during%20his%20brief%20but%20electric%20stay%20at%20the%20crease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20Aakash%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20stepping%20out%20from%20the%20first%20ball%2C%20hitting%20over%20the%20top%2C%20and%20playing%20shots%20everywhere.%20I%20said%20he%20was%20also%20playing%20differently.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAakash%20said%20that%20it%20would%20be%20better%20if%20Virat%20played%20near%20his%20T20I%20career%20strike%20rate%20of%20around%20140%20to%20retain%20his%20consistency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20Virat%20Kohli%20is%20at%20his%20best%3B%20he%20has%20scored%20more%20than%204000%20runs%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20around%20140%2C%20so%20it%20is%20good%20if%20he%20plays%20close%20to%20that.%20If%20he%20tries%20to%20do%20more%20than%20that%2C%20he%20will%20lose%20his%20consistency.%20If%20he%20loses%20his%20consistency%2C%20I%20will%20be%20slightly%20sad%20as%20an%20Indian%20cricket%20fan%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chopra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20is%20the%20highest%20run-getter%20in%20T20Is.%20In%20116%20matches%2C%20he%20has%20scored%204%2C037%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2052.42%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20138.20.%20He%20has%20scored%20a%20century%20and%2037%20fifties%20and%20his%20best%20score%20is%20122*.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAakash%20also%20expressed%20his%20disappointment%20with%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20shot%20selection.%20Rohit%20attempted%20to%20dance%20down%20the%20track%20for%20an%20aggressive%20shot%2C%20but%20was%20cleaned%20up%20by%20Fazalhaq%20Farooqi%20for%20a%20golden%20duck%2C%20his%20second%20duck%20in%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20extremely%20surprising%20the%20way%20Rohit%20got%20out.%20He%20was%20playing%20just%20his%20first%20ball.%20He%20does%20not%20play%20such%20shots.%20The%20ball%20went%20and%20hit%20his%20stumps.%20He%20got%20run%20out%20in%20the%20last%20match%20and%20was%20bowled%20for%20zero%20in%20this%20match.%20He%20has%20not%20scored%20a%20single%20run%20in%20this%20series%20thus%20far%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Aakash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAakash%20said%20that%20Rohit%20will%20have%20to%20score%20some%20runs%20in%20IPL%202024%20and%20Men%20in%20Blue%20need%20the%20starts%20he%20used%20to%20provide%20during%20the%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20at%20home%20last%20year%2C%20during%20which%20he%20scored%20597%20runs%20in%2011%20matches%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%20125.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRun-out%20was%20not%20his%20mistake%20but%20the%20shot%20selection%20was.%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20about%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20form%20and%20ability.%20However%2C%20he%20will%20have%20to%20be%20in%20form%20in%20the%20IPL%20and%20I%20feel%20he%20will%20bat%20like%20this%20only.%20We%20need%2038-40%2C%20the%20runs%20he%20was%20scoring%20in%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20from%20his%20bat%2C%26quot%3B%20concluded%20Aakash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20India%20opted%20to%20field%20first%20and%20troubled%20Afghanistan%20with%20frequent%20wickets.%20Gulbadin%20Naib%20(57%20in%2035%20balls%2C%20with%20five%20fours%20and%20four%20sixes)%20continued%20to%20play%20unbothered%2C%20despite%20wickets%20falling%20at%20the%20other%20end%20and%20made%20an%20attacking%20fifty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShort%20cameos%20from%20Najibullah%20Zadran%20(23%20in%2021%20balls%20with%20a%20boundary%20and%20two%20sixes)%2C%20Karim%20Janat%20(20%20in%2010%20balls%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20and%20Mujeeb%20ur%20Rahman%20(21%20in%20nine%20balls%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes)%20powered%20Afghanistan%20to%20172%20in%20their%2020%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPacer%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20(3%2F32)%20was%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20bowlers%20for%20India%2C%20while%20Ravi%20Bishnoi%20(2%2F39)%20and%20Axar%20(2%2F17)%20also%20bowled%20well%20to%20restrict%20Afghanistan's%20run%20flow.%20Shivam%20Dube%20also%20took%201%2F36%20in%20his%20three%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20chase%20of%20173%2C%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20was%20once%20again%20out%20for%20a%20duck.%20But%20a%20returning%20Virat%20Kohli%20(29%20in%2016%20balls%2C%20with%20five%20fours)%20played%20with%20a%20refreshing%20attacking%20intent%20and%20formed%20a%2057-run%20stand%20with%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal.%20Following%20Virat's%20dismissal%2C%20Yashasvi%20(68%20in%2034%20balls%2C%20with%20five%20fours%20and%20six%20sixes)%20and%20Shivam%20Dube%20(63*%20in%2032%20balls%20with%20five%20fours%20and%20four%20sixes)%20demolished%20the%20Afghanistan%20bowling%20line-up%20with%20their%20hitting%2C%20putting%20up%20a%2092-run%20partnership%20in%20just%2042%20balls.%20Rinku%20Singh%20(9*)%20and%20Shivam%20finished%20off%20things%20to%20give%20India%20a%20six-wicket%20win%20and%20a%20series%20win%20by%202-0%2C%20with%20one%20game%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarim%20Janat%20(2%2F13)%20was%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20bowlers%20for%20Afghanistan.%20Axar%20Patel%20was%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'%20for%20his%20bowling%20spell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705311000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fci58e5a_virat-kohli-bcci_625x300_15_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-afghanistan-t20i-2024%2Fvirat-kohli-will-lose-ex-india-cricketers-big-warning-to-star-batter-on-t20i-return-4865767%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aakash%20Chopra%20said%20that%20it%20would%20be%20better%20if%20Virat%20Kohli%20played%20near%20his%20T20I%20career%20strike%20rate%20of%20around%20140%20to%20retain%20his%20consistency.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22FASTags%20with%20incomplete%20KYC%20to%20be%20deactivated%20post%20Jan%2031%2C%20says%20NHAI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705310998000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2019-12%2F26%2Ffull%2F1577302032-4588.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https