ng%20and%20observing%20the%20rituals%20in%20the%20proposed%20consecration.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98The%20puja%20of%20the%20Ram%20Lala%20is%20done%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20Ramanandi%20tradition%20but%20the%20Trust%20is%20following%20a%20mixed%20tradition%2C%20which%20is%20not%20proper%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Mahant%20said.%20%E2%80%9DWe%20want%20the%20rituals%20and%20worship%20of%20Ram%20Lala%20to%20continue%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20Ramanandi%20traditions%20but%20the%20Trust%20has%20ignored%20our%20plea%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20emphasised%20that%20the%20%E2%80%99tilak%E2%80%99%20and%20other%20symbols%20in%20the%20Ramanandi%20traditions%20were%20different%20from%20other%20sects.%20This%20sect%20has%20been%20responsible%20for%20conducting%20the%20prayers%20in%20the%20make-shift%20temple%20that%20has%20existed%20in%20Ayodhya%20since%20December%201992%20and%20before%20that%2C%20on%20the%20Ram%20chabutra%2C%20the%20outer%20courtyard%20of%20the%20Babri%20masjid%2C%20when%20the%20mosque%20still%20stood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20newspaper%20also%20reports%20that%20the%20Nirmohi%20Akhara%20had%20pleaded%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20it%20should%20also%20be%20given%20the%20right%20to%20hold%20puja%20and%20other%20rituals%20in%20the%20Ram%20Temple.%20The%20court%20had%20said%20that%20the%20Trust%2C%20which%20would%20look%20after%20the%20Ram%20Temple%2C%20might%2C%20if%20it%20wanted%2C%20give%20it%20the%20right.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amarujala.com%2Fram-mandir%2Fayodhya-ram-mandir-champat-rai-said-that-temple-belongs-to-ramanand-sect-not-to-shaiva-shakta-and-sannyasis-2024-01-08%3FpageId%3D1%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3EAmar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EUjala%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Te