%20could%20be%20built%20in%2018%20months.%20The%20idea%20was%20that%20it%20would%20be%20built%20in%20three%20years.%20If%20we%20start%20from%20July%202020%2C%20then%20with%202023%2C%20three%20and%20a%20half%20years%20have%20passed.%20Now%2C%20if%20someone%20decides%20that%20it%20will%20be%20completed%20within%20a%20year%2C%20then%20after%20a%20year%2C%20he%20will%20have%20to%20tell%20that%20so%20much%20is%20still%20incomplete%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAmar%20Ujala.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20can%20read%20more%20about%20it%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fits-a-ram-mandir-ramanand-tradition-to-be-followed-temple-trusts-secy-remarks-draw-criticism%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705302056000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11102438%2FScreenshot-2024-01-11-at-10.24.0.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fram-lala-ramanandi-nirmohi-akhali-temple%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reports%20say%20the%20Nirmohi%20Akhada%2C%20a%20key%20player%20in%20this%20context%20and%20an%20original%20litigant%20in%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi-Babri%20Masjid%20title%20dispute%20is%20feeling%20sidelined%20and%20saying%20the%20'tilak'%20and%20other%20symbols%20in%20the%20Ramanandi%20traditions%20were%20different%20from%20other%20sects.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fram-lala-ramanandi-nirmohi-akhali-temple%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20are%20solid-fuel%20missiles%2C%20and%20why%20is%20North%20Korea%20developing%20them%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705301636000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106857006%2Cimgsize-1466445.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.