2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67977761.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67977761.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jobs%20in%20Israel%3A%20Labour%20Activists%2C%20Trade%20Unions%20Raise%20Concerns%20Over%20No%20Protections%20for%20Indian%20Workers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F05093056%2F917079141_8136ef6623_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Labour%20activists%20and%20trade%20unions%20have%20raised%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20recruitment%20of%20Indian%20workers%20for%20jobs%20in%20Israel%2C%20as%20officials%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Haryana%20are%20set%20to%20screen%20applicants%20for%20these%20positions.%20Activists%20argue%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20is%20bypassing%20normal%20protections%20it%20normally%20employs%20for%20Indian%20labour%20going%20abroad%20to%20conflict%20zones%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fno-protections-for-migrant-workers-being-recruited-by-the-government-for-israel-labour-activists-to-move-court%2Farticle67740473.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520workers%2520heading%2520to%2520Israel%2Ccountries%2520and%2520other%2520labour%2520markets.%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20workers%20will%20not%20even%20be%20required%20to%20register%20themselves%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98e-migrate%E2%80%99%20portal%20run%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%20Several%20government%20ministries%20and%20agencies%20have%20disclaimed%20any%20responsibility%20for%20the%20welfare%20and%20safety%20of%20the%20workers%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Haryana%20government%20invited%20applications%20from%20construction%20workers%20for%20job%20openings%20in%20Israel.%20The%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Flatest%2Fin-focus%2Fstory%2Fharyana-govt-plans-to-recruit-10000-skilled-workers-for-jobs-in-israel-409692-2023-12-16%5C%22%3Eplans%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmeerut%2Fup-govt-plans-to-send-10000-construction-workers-to-israel%2Farticleshow%2F106362374.cms%5C%22%3Esend%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20least%2010%2C000%20workers%20to%20the%20conflict-hit%20nation.%20The%20workers%20will%20be%20selected%20by%20the%20National%20Skills%20Development%20Corporation%20(NSDC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20jobs%20promise%20attractive%20salaries%20of%20approximately%20Rs%201.37%20lakh%20per%20month%2C%20but%20lack%20details%20on%20contractual%20protections.%20Accommodation%2C%20food%2C%20and%20medical%20insurance%20costs%20will%20be%20deducted%20from%20the%20salary.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20workers%20are%20expected%20to%20pay%20for%20their%20own%20tickets%2C%20and%20the%20NSDC%20charges%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20worker%20as%20facilitation%20fees%2C%20the%20daily%20reported%2C%20citing%20official%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActivists%20have%20called%20the%20move%20%E2%80%9Cinhumane%E2%80%9D%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20fast-track%20the%20recruitment%20of%20Indian%20construction%20workers%2C%20nurses%20and%20caregivers%20even%20while%20Israeli%20operations%20continue%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%20will%20put%20them%20in%20harm%E2%80%99s%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20step%20is%20against%20Indian%20ethos.%20We%20are%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20Israel.%20We%20are%20concerned%20about%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20All%20India%20Trade%20Union%20Congress%20(AITUC)%20general%20secretary%20Amarjeet%20Kaur%20told%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20trade%20unions%20now%20plan%20to%20approach%20the%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20seems%20to%20be%20passing%20the%20buck%20on%20this%20matter.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20various%20government%20agencies%20formally%20distanced%20themselves%20from%20the%20documents%20themselves%2C%20put%20out%20in%20the%20name%20of%20NSDC%20International%2C%20government%20sources%20confirmed%20that%20the%20recruitment%20process%20will%20begin%20this%20week%20with%20interviews%20and%20screening%20in%20several%20cities%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%2C%20NSDC%20chief%20executive%20Ved%20Mani%20Tiwari%20told%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fi%3E%20that%20the%20advertisements%20had%20been%20issued%20by%20the%20state%20governments%2C%20not%20by%20the%20NSDC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20no%20mandate%20for%20Israel%20or%20for%20the%20employers.%20We%20are%20not%20a%20recruiting%20company.%20Some%20state%20governments%20have%20invited%20applications%20for%20jobs%20in%20Israel%20and%20our%20mandate%20is%20to%20provide%20skill%20training%20for%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tiwari%20told%20the%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Labour%20Ministry%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20plans%2C%20as%20did%20Haryana%20Labour%20Minister%20Anoop%20Dhanak.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20MEA%20that%20monitors%20such%20migration%20of%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20said%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20MEA%20also%20declined%20to%20reply%20to%20a%20detailed%20list%20of%20questions%20sent%20by%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Hindu%20%3C%2Fi%3Easking%20what%20kind%20of%20assurances%20were%20being%20requested%20from%20the%20Israeli%20labour%20agency%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Population%20and%20Immigration%20Authority%2C%20known%20as%20PIBA.%20Officials%20said%20that%20the%20recruitment%20was%20taking%20place%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9CB2B%E2%80%9D%20or%20business-to-business%20arrangement%2C%20offering%20little%20clarity%20on%20who%20will%20actually%20be%20responsible%20for%20the%20eventual%20fate%20of%20the%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20all%20workers%20going%20to%20conflict%20zones%20or%20places%20without%20sufficient%20labour%20protections%20are%20required%20to%20register%20with%20the%20MEA%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98e-migrate%E2%80%99%20portal.%20However%2C%20Israel%20is%20not%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98e-migrate%E2%80%99%20system%20for%20conflict%20zones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPIBA%2C%20the%20Israeli%20immigration%20agency%2C%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20specific%20questions%20about%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20workers%2C%20but%20sources%20said%20that%20they%20would%20proceed%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20an%20agreement%20signed%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20the%20daily%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705300259000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F05093056%2F917079141_8136ef6623_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjobs-in-israel-labour-activists-trade-unions-raise-concerns-over-no-protections-for-indian-workers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20present%2C%20all%20workers%20going%20to%20conflict%20zones%20or%20places%20without%20sufficient%20labour%20protections%20are%20required%20to%20register%20with%20the%20MEA's%20'e-migrate'%20portal.%20However%2C%20Israel%20is%20not%20part%20of%20the%20'e-migrate'%20system%20for%20conflict%20zones%2C%20the%20'Hindu'%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjobs-in-israel-labour-activists-trade-unions-raise-concerns-over-no-protections-for-indian-workers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chinese%20officials%20say%20Covid-19%20infections%20may%20rebound%20in%20country%20in%20January%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705300046000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106856002%2Cimgsize-49560.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%